<html lang="en-US">

<div class="w3-container" appml-data="appml.php?model=model_cd_from_json">

<div appml-include-html="inc_listcommands_nofilter.htm"></div>
<table class="w3-table-all">

    <th>Artist</th>
    <th>Price</th>
  </tr>
  <tr appml-repeat="records">
    <td>{{Title}}</td>
    <td>{{Artist}}</td>
    <td>{{Price}}</td>

</table>
</div>

</body>
</html>
